      <title>Shein 将在电子商务打击行动中接受欧盟消费者法调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/shein-to-face-eu-consumer-law-probe-under-e-commerce-crackdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由中国创办的大型在线交易市场 Shein 面临潜在的罚款，欧盟即将对其在销售非法产品方面是否遵守消费者法律展开调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/shein-to-face-eu-consumer-law-probe-under-e-commerce-crackdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 12:34:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普和马斯克威胁关闭美国国际开发署，为中国打开大门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/trump-and-musk-s-usaid-shut-down-threat-opens-door-for-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界各地的慈善机构、外交官和外国官员都在疯狂地试图弄清楚，在特朗普政府攻击美国全球影响力基石的背景下，美国这个为非洲拯救生命的艾滋病项目和为乌克兰提供资金等各种援助的机构将会发生什么。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/trump-and-musk-s-usaid-shut-down-threat-opens-door-for-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 11:50:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国议员要求罗伯特·肯尼迪 (RFK Jr.) 远离疫苗决策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/us-lawmakers-ask-rfk-jr-to-stay-away-from-vaccine-decisions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国民主党议员要求小罗伯特·F·肯尼迪（Robert F. Kennedy Jr.）如果被任命为卫生与公众服务部部长，不要参与所有与疫苗相关的决定，因为他的家人可能会从反疫苗诉讼中受益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/us-lawmakers-ask-rfk-jr-to-stay-away-from-vaccine-decisions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 11:09:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
