    <item>
      <title>印尼将把 610 亿美元国有资产转入新基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/indonesia-set-to-shift-61-billion-of-state-assets-into-new-fund</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚准备将至少 610 亿美元的国有资产转移到一个强大的新投资基金，该基金直接向总统普拉博沃·苏比安托 (Prabowo Subianto) 汇报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/indonesia-set-to-shift-61-billion-of-state-assets-into-new-fund</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 10:08:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
